---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Justin Helmer — Principal Engineer.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-heading">About</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p>Started in frontend design and JavaScript, then moved into full-stack development, server-side systems, and infrastructure. Spent several years building AI-powered optimization systems before the current wave — real-time decisioning, model serving, experimentation platforms.</p>
    <p>From there into large-scale platform engineering: mobile infrastructure at Macy's, cross-acquisition system integration at Intellimize, and most recently the hard problems at scale — authorization, permissioning, real-time services, and now AI agent infrastructure.</p>
    <p>Principal Engineer. Seventeen years across the full stack. Currently focused on building the systems that will support the next generation of builders.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }
</style>
